    "QuantumMob/Q3", "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "QuantumScramblingCircuit[a, {p, t}, {s1, s2, ...}] generate the quantum \
circuit realization of a(t) := u^\\[Dagger] (t) a u(t) for the study quantum \
information scrambling, where a is a local unitary operator and u(t) is a \
(random) time-evolution operator. QuantumScramblingCircuit[k, {p, t}, {s1, \
s2, ...}] assumes a := Xk, where Xk is the Pauli-X operator on the k^th \
qubit.", "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> 
